    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "2.音系介绍 ",
        "text_level": 1,
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "徐州方言音系系统如下：",
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（1）声母共23个，包括零声母在内：",
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "table",
        "img_path": "images/0d8c4701b16bb1db6013b8a7745e63709e96b13c8efc3bef7da59e093f0b9611.jpg",
        "table_caption": [],
        "table_footnote": [],
        "table_body": "<html><body><table><tr><td>p</td><td>p</td><td>m</td><td>f</td><td>V</td><td>t</td><td>t</td><td>n</td><td>1</td><td>ts</td><td>ts`</td><td>S</td></tr><tr><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td>ts</td><td>ts'</td><td>S</td><td>Z</td><td>tc</td><td>te</td><td></td><td>k</td><td>k</td><td>X</td><td>0</td><td></td></tr></table></body></html>",
        "page_idx": 2
